                    The NYU School of Professional Studies Diploma in Paralegal Studies has been suspended and will not be accepting new students at this time. Current students will be able to complete their studies and to earn their diploma in a timely manner. We appreciate your patience as we work to develop new programming to meet the needs of professionals in this evolving field.
